OL,6,FMacCormack is the fourth man to be
OL,7,Fsentenced following a sexual
OL,8,Fexploitation investigation conducted
OL,9,Fby the PSNI's modern slavery and human
OL,10,Ftrafficking unit.
OL,12,FThe court heard the victims were
OL,13,Fheroin addicts and MacCormack would
OL,14,Fexploit their vulnerability to force
OL,15,Fthem into prostitution in exchange for
OL,16,Fhim supplying them with drugs.
