OL,11,FMiskelly said MacCormack ensured the
OL,12,Fyoung females became dependent upon
OL,13,Fhim for their supply of heroin.
OL,15,F"He groomed and encouraged them to
OL,16,Fbecome involved in sex work, and
OL,17,Fcontrolled their prostitution by
OL,18,Farranging meetings with sex-buyers,
OL,19,Ftransporting them to and from
OL,20,Fappointments," she said.
